title: your account is in the process of transferring
body:
Hey. My smurf account got this message : your account is in the process of transferring  and i dont know what now? IGN: My barrels 

Region: EUNE.

replies.body:
If this was not intended then there's a possibility another user may have gotten access to the account.  Don't worry though, we can help!  Reach out to us through an [account recovery form](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new?ticket_form_id=72416) so our account team can assist with recovery and reparations.  

In the meantime, definitely check our[ account protection](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201751664-Protecting-Your-Account) guide to make sure your information in/out of League is secure.
